    <string name="question_six">6. How to Logout?</string>
    <string name="answer_one">Go to the Add Transaction page by tapping the add icon in the navigation menu. Choose income or expense, input the amount, select the date, and pick the relevant category.</string>
    <string name="answer_two">On the Recommendations page, explore the \'Insights\' and \'Tips and Tricks\' sections. Provide your monthly income data to get accurate insights and suggestions for better financial management.</string>
    <string name="answer_three">Navigate to the Account page and select Update Profile. Modify your username and tap Save to apply the changes.</string>
    <string name="answer_four">Go to the Account page and select Update Profile. Choose \'Update\' to pick a new picture or \'Delete\' to remove it. Tap Save to finalize the changes.</string>
    <string name="answer_five">Tap \'Forgot Password\' on the login page. Enter your email and tap \'Change Password\'. Check your email for a reset link, follow it, and create a new password.</string>
    <string name="answer_six">Navigate to the Account page and tap \'Logout\'. You will be logged out of the application.</string>

